Figure Caption: The XRD patterns of the Fe40Mn28Ni32−xCrx(x=4, 12, 18, 24) alloys. The XRD patterns of the Fe40Mn28Ni32−xCrx(x=4, 12, 18) were taken in cold-rolled and annealed state. The XRD pattern of the Fe40Mn28Ni8Cr24alloy was taken in homogenized state.

The SEM-BSE images of the Fe40Mn28Ni32−xCrx(x=4, 12, 18, 24) alloys: a — x=4; b — x=12; c — x=18; d — x=24. The images of the Fe40Mn28Ni32−xCrx(x=4, 12, 18) were taken in cold-rolled and annealed state. The image of the Fe40Mn28Ni8Cr24alloy was taken in homogenized state.
